Plosurin 
=====================

Plosurin - Perl 5 implementation of Closure Templates


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Regexp::Grammars;
 HTTP::Server::Simple::WebDAO;
 Perl6::Pod::Lib
 Perl6::Pod

